IAAJ"><i>Democratization in the South: The Jagged Wave</i></a>. Manchester University Press. p.&#160;11. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0719049423" title="Special:BookSources/0719049423">0719049423</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAncient+Rome&amp;rft.au=White%2C+Gordon&amp;rft.aufirst=Robin&amp;rft.aulast=Luckham&amp;rft.btitle=Democratization+in+the+South%3A+The+Jagged+Wave&amp;rft.date=1996&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=0719049423&amp;rft.pages=11&amp;rft.pub=Manchester+University+Press&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FDemocratization_in_the_South.html%3Fid%3DRMDnAAAAIAAJ&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation book">Sellers, Mortimer N. (1994). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books/about/American_Republicanism.html?id=zN7lgzjettgC"><i>American Republicanism: Roman Ideology in the United States Constitution</i></a>. NYU Press. p.&#160;90. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0814780059" title="Special:BookSources/0814780059">0814780059</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAncient+Rome&amp;rft.aufirst=Mortimer+N.&amp;rft.aulast=Sellers&amp;rft.btitle=American+Republicanism%3A+Roman+Ideology+in+the+United+States+Constitution&amp;rft.date=1994&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=0814780059&amp;rft.pages=90&amp;rft.pub=NYU+Press&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FAmerican_Republicanism.html%3Fid%3DzN7lgzjettgC&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Ao